Missing features
================

* Fuller .mtl file support; see http://paulbourke.net/dataformats/mtl/
* Phong etc shading.
* Fix line plotting bugs:
    - z-lines near the horizon are botched.
* Fix triangle plotting bugs:
    - some polys appear as protruding horizontal lines, why?
        - see top of teapot for an example
        - for example, this plot will fail: vertices: (338.29, 110.40), (337.79, 111.34), (371.32, 108.36)
        - either halfpoly can fail
	- this looks awfully like a int/float, division, rounding problem that causes the deltas to be huge
